Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Cup of Sealed Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I open my reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal of Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Temple of the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I gather these three Magic Cards together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Summon the Mystical Beast, who protects the secrets of the alter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The guardian of the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scorpion God that shall {\i1}devour{\i0} your Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your glorious form before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Mystical Beast, Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\N Another monster just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mystical Beast Selket exists to guard the sacred card sealed in the ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred card?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, the card you sealed in that ark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's the God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Summon the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical Beast Selket is only a demigod who protects the {\i1}true god{\i0} within the shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you freakin' serious...?!\N I've only got 200 Life Points left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand up to such a powerful Monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried so hard to push Malik into the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}, is there anything my brother can do to win this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} has on the field don't stand a chance against Selket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't think of something fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik will destroy every single one of Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Wall Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yugi...\N That ark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra is in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His God Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I guess he {\b0}is{\b1} Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why don't I consider him the real Malik...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik, why did you place the God Card in my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid... you must play my role more realistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is a Ra copy card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A duplicate card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right! With the Ghouls' "Rare Card Duplication Technology",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even God Cards can be mass-produced!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But of course, my card is the {\b0}original{\b1} card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed, even the copy card is the type of card that {\b0}chooses{\b1} its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the past, a number of Ghouls experimented by playing with decks of copy God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as a result, some were killed the moment they played them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some even went crazy and lost their minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps this is what they call "God's Curse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After more experiments, one fact became clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Copy God Cards react to the {\b0}hearts{\b1} of their wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But a descendant of the Tomb Guardians that have thrived for 3,000 years might succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid, you have lived {\b0}among{\b1} the Tomb Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If your heart as grown strong enough as a result,\N you should be able to control the god!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm very sorry, Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't {\b0}need{\b1} God's help to win this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Selket was Summoned using a Ritual Magic Card, it cannot attack this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefor my turn shall now end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a bet here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have a high-level Monster to stop his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even have a Magic Card to turn this around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my Monsters go to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he at least has a chance to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Jounouchi!\N I attack you with Mystical Beast Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your target is Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's {\b0}eating{\b1} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it is an unpleasant sight to behold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that is Selket's Special Ability, which has now activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selket takes enemies inside itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and adds half of their Attack Points to its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3700 Attack Points!\N And it changed to a different shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster with the ability to add its enemy's power to its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna get stronger and stronger if he doesn't do something soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... I couldn't do a thing this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Selket attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next sacrifice shall be the Insect Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insect Queen has been defeated!\N It now absorbs her Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Haga...\N Your card was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in the card you draw next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!\N I can't! I just can't watch anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you run, Shizuka!\N Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might lose this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to watch until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found light in the deep darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A light called {\i1}courage{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter what happens, don't you run back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light in the deep darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That "light" is the story of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I met the Ishtar couple,\N I was given light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a deep, dark world with no contact to the outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And one night I accidentally overheard the secret of the Ishtar family...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the fate of the Tomb Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Rod\N and the Millennium Tauk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both the Millennium Items and the Pharaoh's memories that sleep in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Protecting them is the duty of us Tomb Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must not fail to pass down this 3,000 year history to the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear, if we are not blessed with a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Rishid becomes ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let's accept him as our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that child is not a true member of our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But perhaps God meant for him to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps the Rite of the Tomb Guardians could be performed on Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's name her Ishizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The successor of the Tomb Guardians must be a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid... I have something important to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you turn ten, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we would like to make you a member of our tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to do that, you must undergo the Rite of the Tomb Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rite of the Tomb Guardians...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Rite of the Tomb Guardians is a cruel trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite that...\N Despite that, are you prepared to undergo the ritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! So by doing it, I can become your {\b0}real{\b1} son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've done well!\N It's a perfectly healthy boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...! Please take care... of your little brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The successor of the Tomb Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pedigree of darkness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow! You're amazing, Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How the hell did this happen when you were {\b0}right{\b1} by his side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If anything happens to Malik,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll rip out your {\b0}heart{\b1} and tear it to {\b0}pieces{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order for our family to live on the next generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's not {\b0}you{\b1} we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's {\b0}Malik{\b1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you {\b0}dare{\b1} leave this room until Malik regains his conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sorry... You're always getting beat up because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you just address me as your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always thought\N of you as my big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik, here is your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why not?\N You should at least have a little soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...\N Have you ever seen my father's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got the markings of the Rite of the Tomb Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The successor of the Tomb Guardians 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had the secrets of the Pharaoh's memories carved onto his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he must protect\N these secrets with his {\b0}life{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to undergo the ritual on my birthday next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say the pain is so bad you'll scream for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really scared of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think I can take it!\N I might even {\b0}die{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?!\N Why do I have to go through with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik, please be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will ask Lord Ishtar to allow me to take the ritual in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have been\N prepared for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}You'll{\b1} undergo the ritual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it's an unreasonable request!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Lord Malik is too scared to take the ritual himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt very bad for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will protect the secrets of the Tomb Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only have one wish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I wish is to undergo the ritual and be called your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nonsense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just a {\b0}servant{\b1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you ever talk of our secrets again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll cut off your miserable {\b0}tongue{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of my sight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Help me, Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid, {\i1}help{\i0} me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RISHID!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...! My dear little brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...! It really hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to change your bandages...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't {\i1}touch{\i0} me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please {\i1}tell{\i0} me, Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do I {\i1}hate{\i0} for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot share the pain that you are suffering from, Lord Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall swear allegiance to your family with this scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will eliminate Yugi and anyone else who stands in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is our revenge on the nameless Pharaoh...\N of the clan of the Tomb Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As you wish, Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up your hopes of defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mystical Beast Selket keeps growing by absorbing my Monster's Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It grows into a stronger Monster each time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its Attack Power is already 4900!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good... I don't have any cards that can turn this around...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll switch my Fisherman into Defense Mode and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite this situation,\N you actually plan to continue Dueling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's insulting, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be useless to continue fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have something\N I want to accomplish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll fight on until my Life hits 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm sure you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard Jounouchi may try to turn this situation around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is just one\N match Jounouchi can't turn around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi can't win this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that... look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way he can win the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his fighting spirit still hasn't disappeared from his eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the eyes of someone prepared for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension on this battlefield reflects both of their Duelist's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both honored\N they met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their fighting spirit is flooding\N throughout the entire field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens in this Duel,\N these two will not stop fighting until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the Legendary Fisherman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now grow, Mystical Beast Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please forgive me, Kajiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't protect your card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Jounouchi, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your {\i1}last{\i0} one, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Malik attacks on his next turn, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose I should at least {\b0}praise{\b1} you for fighting as a lab rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this point, Jounouchi's chances of winning have fallen to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well done, Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's your victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What you can see, but can't see..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a funny feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little while ago, I reached the point where I was resigned to losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just then, when winning or losing didn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's like I saw something\N I couldn't see before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I figure it out sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must have been the heat of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik brainwashed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He forced me to fight my friend in a Duel to the death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pointless battle that\N only hurt our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive the bastard who set up that Duel and forced us to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go ahead and {\i1}curse{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a match is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That anger is not enough to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this Duel started,\N I really hated your guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've lost that hatred now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I tried to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible it felt when that bastard took over my mind and implanted his memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't use any cheap tricks and fought me fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may lose to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but while fighting against you in this Duel, it became one of the best I've had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not know your reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I do know one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the guy who did that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}aren't{\i0} Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the wielder of God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His strategies are much different than the ones I faced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And more importantly, I don't feel a Power of Darkness coming from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An enemy you can see, but can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's the {\i1}real{\i0} Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this goes on, my plan will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my identity as Malik is discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to probe Kaiba's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and find out if he was the previous wielder of the Millennium Rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I won't be able to learn the secrets of that palette...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What utter {\i1}bullshit{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Millennium Rod is {\i1}proof{\i0} that I am Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel shall continue as I have foreseen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and {\i1}no one{\i0} listens to the words of a {\i1}loser{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him off, Mystical Beast Selket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is as far as I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N -Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't attack him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, Lord Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill Jounouchi...\N by the hands of the God Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order for our plan to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you must prove you are the wielder of a God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are {\b0}Malik{\b1}, Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summon Ra from\N within the ark in the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use the Counterfeit God Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After finally Summoning the third God Card, Winged Sun Dragon of Ra,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi can't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all over, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra won't attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, a huge thunderstorm roars across the Battle Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this "God's wrath"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ra's Anger!\N Stand Up, Jounouchi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
